 6ï¸âƒ£ IPv4 vs IPv6

 IPv4

â†’ 32-bit address
â†’ 4 octets (each 8 bits)
â†’ Example: `192.168.1.10`
â†’ Total bits = 32

 IPv6

â†’ 128-bit address
â†’ Example: `2001:db8::1`
â†’ Zyada IP addresses available
â†’ Future ready

