OSI Model network communication ko 7 layers me divide karta hai, taaki samajhna aur troubleshoot karna easy ho. Simple words me ğŸ‘‡

1. Physical Layer
Wire, cable, signals ka kaam. Data bits (0/1) me travel karta hai.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: Ethernet cable, voltage signals

2. Data Link Layer
Direct device-to-device communication. Error check + MAC address use hota hai.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: Switch, MAC address

3. Network Layer
Data ko route karta hai source se destination tak.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: IP address, Router

4. Transport Layer
Data ko chunks (segments) me todta hai, reliable delivery ensure karta hai.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: TCP (reliable), UDP (fast)

5. Session Layer
Sender aur receiver ke beech session start, maintain aur close karta hai.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: Login session

6. Presentation Layer
Data ka format samajhne layak banata hai (encrypt, compress, translate).
ğŸ‘‰ Example: Encryption, JPEG/MP3 format

7. Application Layer
User ke bilkul closest layer. Yahin se user network use karta hai.
ğŸ‘‰ Example: Browser, Email, HTTP, FTP

